## Objective

To understand how modern websites are built using reusable UI components by breaking down a popular website into smaller parts and analyzing its structure.

## Selected Website

Example: Amazon Homepage (you can replace with any site like Flipkart, Instagram)

## Identified Components
Header / Navbar
Logo (Amazon logo)
Search bar
Location selector
Account & Lists
Cart icon
Main Banner / Hero Section
Large promotional images
Sliding carousel (offers, deals)
Category Section
Boxes showing categories like electronics, fashion, home
Each box contains images + links
Product Cards
Product image
Title
Price
Ratings
“Add to Cart” button
Deals Section
Limited-time offers
Discount highlights
Countdown timers (sometimes)
Footer
Links (About, Contact, Help)
Social media links
Copyright info
